             was indicted <rs id="t18150215-129-off766" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18150215-129-off766" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18150215-129-off766" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniniously stealing on the <rs id="t18150215-129-cd767" type="crimeDate">20th of January</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18150215-129-off766 t18150215-129-cd767"></join>, one shawl. value 3 s. and a glass tumbler, value 6 d.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18150215-129-victim1086" type="victimName">
                     William 
                     Holmes
                  <interp inst="t18150215-129-victim1086" type="surname" value="Holmes"></interp>
